data.description: $15,000 price IMPROVEMENT! Welcome to your Cul-de-sac, greenbelt dream home in Longs Creek! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence offers over 3600 square feet of space. NEW A/C + water heater, both less than one year old, and NEW paint on kitchen cabinets! Recently installed luxury vinyl planking throughout, with ZERO carpet. The entertainer's kitchen boasts ample counter space, complemented by a formal dining area, and dual-living spaces, providing plenty of room for your family to relax. All bedrooms are conveniently located on the second floor, ensuring easy access and a seamless living experience. Step outside to the massive backyard oasis, an entertainer's paradise with space for a pool! Embrace unforgettable gatherings on the deck, surrounded by mature trees this home promises utmost privacy, this home offers easy access to Bulverde Rd. and 1604, along with nearby amenities and highly-rated schools. Running errands, or grocery shopping is a breeze, with HEB just 2 minutes away. Priced to sell, this extraordinary property won't last - a perfect blend of convenience and comfort. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity!
